{"word":"H8598 - תַּפּוּחַ - tappûwach - tap-poo'-akh - Apple","slug":"H8598","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">תַּפּוּחַ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tappûwach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tap-poo'-akh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Apple"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05EA;&#x05BC;&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05D7; - tappu&#x0302;ach</b> - <i>tap-poo'-akh</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H5301\">H5301</a>; an <i>apple</i> (from its <i>fragrance</i>), that is, the fruit or the tree (probably including others of the <i>pome</i> order, as the quince, the orange, etc.): - apple (tree). See also <a href=\"#/H1054\">H1054</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4646\">H4646</a>, <a href=\"#/H4647\">H4647</a>, <a href=\"#/H5300\">H5300</a>, <a href=\"#/H5301\">H5301</a>, <a href=\"#/H5302\">H5302</a>, <a href=\"#/H5304\">H5304</a>, <a href=\"#/H5306\">H5306</a>, <a href=\"#/H5887\">H5887</a>, <a href=\"#/H8599\">H8599</a>"}]}